      "description": "This 996.1 Carrera features the high-revving M96 3.4L flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts for precise turn-in. It benefits from a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recent rear main seal replacement, ensuring drivetrain integrity. The factory Brembo monobloc calipers provide consistent thermal management under load. While the Arctic Silver finish shows minor road patina, the mechanical fundamentals are robust, making this an ideal driver's car for those seeking an analog flat-six experience.",
